{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"42":{"eng-name":"Model Behavior of the Prophet (Kitab Al-Sunnah)","ara-name":"كتاب السنة"}},"section_detail":{"42":{"hadithnumber_first":4596,"hadithnumber_last":4772,"arabicnumber_first":4596,"arabicnumber_last":4772}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":4718,"arabicnumber":4718,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن اسماعيل، حدثنا حماد، عن ثابت، عن انس، ان رجلا، قال يا رسول الله اين ابي قال \" ابوك في النار \" . فلما قفى قال \" ان ابي واباك في النار","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Muslim (203)"}],"reference":{"book":42,"hadith":123},"chapter":{"id":18,"ara-name":"باب فِي ذَرَارِيِّ الْمُشْرِكِينَ","eng-name":"The Offspring Of Polytheists","isFirstHadith":false}}]}